  <h2>What We Do</h2>
  <p>Logistryx publishes independent reviews and buying guides for home EV chargers and smart home technology. Our goal is simple: help UK homeowners make confident, well-informed purchasing decisions without wading through marketing fluff.</p>

  <h2>Our Approach</h2>
  <p>We research every product thoroughly before recommending it. We look at real-world performance, not just manufacturer specs. We explain things in plain English — not jargon. And we're honest about trade-offs: if a product is great but expensive, we'll say so. If a cheaper option is good enough, we'll tell you that too.</p>

  <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
  <p>Logistryx earns a small commission when you purchase products through links on our site. This is how we keep our content free. We only recommend products we genuinely believe are worth buying — the commission structure does not influence our editorial opinions.</p>
  <p>We're participants in the Amazon Associates UK programme, as well as other affiliate programmes.</p>

